ockholm]], Sweden}}\n|\n|-\n|31\n|{{no2}}Loss\n|25\u20136\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|BUL}} [[Kubrat Pulev]]\n|SD\n|12\n|7 May 2016\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|GER}} {{small|[[Barclaycard Arena (Hamburg)|Barclaycard Arena]], [[Hamburg]], Germany}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|For vacant European heavyweight title}}\n|-\n|30\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|25\u20135\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|HUN}} Andras Csomor\n|TKO\n|2 (8), {{small|2:08}}\n|9 Jan 2016\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|GER}} {{small|Baden-Arena, [[Offenburg]], Germany}}\n|\n|-\n|29\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|24\u20135\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|CRO}} Jakov Gospic\n|TKO\n|3 (8), {{small|2:23}}\n|[[Anthony Joshua vs. Dillian Whyte|12 Dec 2015]]\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[The O2 Arena]], London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|28\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|23\u20135\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|HUN}} Peter Erdos\n|TKO\n|5 (8), {{small|1:01}}\n|5 Dec 2015\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|GER}} {{small|Inselparkhalle, [[Hamburg]], Germany}}\n|\n|-\n|27\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|22\u20135\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|BRA}} Marcelo Luiz Nascimento\n|PTS\n|10\n|26 Sep 2015\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|The SSE Arena Wembley, London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|26\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|21\u20135\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|GEO}} Beka Lobjanidze\n|{{abbr|KO|Knockout}}\n|1 (10), {{small|0:29}}\n|24 Jul 2015\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[The SSE Arena Wembley]], London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|25\n|{{no2}}Loss\n|20\u20135\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Tyson Fury]]\n|RTD\n|10 (12), {{small|3:00}}\n|29 Nov 2014\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|ExCeL, London, England}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Lost European and WBO International heavyweight titles;<br>For vacant British heavyweight title}}\n|-\n|24\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|20\u20134\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA