litschko vs. Dereck Chisora|18 Feb 2012]]\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|GER}} {{small|[[Olympiahalle]], [[Munich]], Germany}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|For [[list of WBC world champions#Heavyweight|WBC heavyweight title]]}}\n|-\n|17\n|{{no2}}Loss\n|15\u20132\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Robert Helenius]]\n|{{abbr|SD|Split decision}}\n|12\n|3 Dec 2011\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|FIN}} {{small|[[Hartwall Arena]], [[Helsinki]], Finland}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|For [[World Boxing Association|WBA]] Inter-Continental, [[World Boxing Organization|WBO]] Inter-Continental, and vacant [[list of European Boxing Union heavyweight champions|European heavyweight titles]]}}\n|-\n|16\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|15\u20131\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|LIT}} Remigijus Ziausys\n|PTS\n|6\n|11 Nov 2011\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|North Bridge Leisure Centre, [[Halifax, West Yorkshire|Halifax]], England}}\n|\n|-\n|15\n|{{no2}}Loss\n|14\u20131\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Tyson Fury]]\n|{{abbr|UD|Unanimous decision}}\n|12\n|23 Jul 2011\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|Wembley Arena, London, England}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Lost British and [[Commonwealth Boxing Council|Commonwealth]] heavyweight titles}}\n|-\n|14\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|14\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Sam Sexton]]\n|TKO\n|9 (12), {{small|2:53}}\n|18 Sep 2010\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[LG Arena (Birmingham)|LG Arena]], [[Birmingham]], England}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Retained [[British Boxing Board of Control|British]] [[heavyweight]] title;<br>Won [[list of Commonwealth Boxing Council champions#Heavyweight|Commonwealth heavyweight title]]}}\n|-\n|13\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|13\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Danny Williams (boxer)|Danny Williams]]\n|TKO\n|2 (12), {{small|1:41}}\n|15 May 2010\n|style=\"text-align: