to\n|PTS\n|10\n|26 Sep 2015\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|The SSE Arena Wembley, London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|26\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|21\u20135\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|GEO}} Beka Lobjanidze\n|{{abbr|KO|Knockout}}\n|1 (10), {{small|0:29}}\n|24 Jul 2015\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[The SSE Arena Wembley]], London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|25\n|{{no2}}Loss\n|20\u20135\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Tyson Fury]]\n|RTD\n|10 (12), {{small|3:00}}\n|29 Nov 2014\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|ExCeL, London, England}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Lost European and WBO International heavyweight titles;<br>For vacant British heavyweight title}}\n|-\n|24\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|20\u20134\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Kevin Johnson (boxer)|Kevin Johnson]]\n|UD\n|12\n|15 Feb 2014\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|Copper Box Arena, London, England}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Retained WBA International and WBO International heavyweight titles}}\n|-\n|23\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|19\u20134\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|CZE}} [[Ond\u0159ej P\u00e1la]]\n|TKO\n|3 (12), {{small|2:25}}\n|30 Nov 2013\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|Copper Box Arena, London, England}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Retained WBO International heavyweight title;<br>Won vacant WBA International heavyweight title}}\n|-\n|22\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|18\u20134\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|GER}} [[Edmund Gerber]]\n|TKO\n|5 (12), {{small|2:55}}\n|21 Sep 2013\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[Copper Box Arena]], London, England}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|Won vacant European heavyweight title}}\n|-\n|21\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|17\u20134\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Malik Scott]]\n|TKO\n|6 (10), {{small|2:56}}\n|20 Jul 2013\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|Wembley Arena, London, England}}\n|