son]]\n|{{abbr|RTD|Corner retirement}}\n|2 (8), {{small|3:00}}\n|6 Dec 2008\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[ExCeL]], London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|7\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|7\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Lee Swaby]]\n|TKO\n|3 (8), {{small|2:45}}\n|26 Sep 2008\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|York Hall, London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|6\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|6\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Shawn McLean\n|TKO\n|6 (8), {{small|3:00}}\n|12 Sep 2008\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[Grosvenor House]], London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|5\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|5\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Sam Sexton]]\n|TKO\n|6 (6), {{small|2:34}}\n|14 Jun 2008\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|York Hall, London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|4\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|4\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} [[Paul Butlin]]\n|PTS\n|4\n|12 Jan 2008\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|York Hall, London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|3\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|3\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} Darren Morgan\n|PTS\n|4\n|13 Oct 2007\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[York Hall]], London, England}}\n|\n|-\n|2\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|2\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} Tony Booth\n|{{abbr|PTS|Points decision}}\n|4\n|7 Apr 2007\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[Millennium Stadium]], [[Cardiff]], Wales}}\n|\n|-\n|1\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|1\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|HUN}} [[Istv\u00e1n Kecsk\u00e9s (boxer)|Istv\u00e1n Kecsk\u00e9s]]\n|{{abbr|TKO|Technical knockout}}\n|2 (4), {{small|1:21}}\n|17 Feb 2007\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|UK}} {{small|[[Wembley Arena]], [[London]], England}}\n|\n|}\n\n==Pay-per-view bouts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Date !! Fight !! Network !! [[Pay-per-view]] buys !! Source(s)\n|-\n| {{dts|2018|December|22|format=dmy}}\n| [[Dillian Whyte]] vs. Dereck Chiso